    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You pull a misterious energy from the body of a creature within range, as you clean their consciousness of illness and negative thought. You end all ranks of one <strong>mental</strong> or <strong>sensory</strong> condition granted by a jutsu or effect of equal rank or lower than what this jutsu was cast.</p><p><strong>At higher ranks:</strong> For each rank above C-rank, increase this jutsu's cost by +3, and the amount of creatures it can affect by +1.</p>",
